poly-app-kodi (0.1.1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Board-agnostic only: the keplerc60 ALSA routing moves to
    poly-kodi-skin-c60portrait (it broke audio on the TC8, whose codec
    differs and whose ALSA defaults are correct).

